{"id":"travel","name":"Travel","file":"travel.org","sourceFile":"blog/travel.org","orgTitle":"游山玩水","sourceBytes":8380,"viewIndex":{"schemaVersion":1,"records":[]},"html":"<main><section><dl><dt>tags </dt><dd><p> <a href=\"古墓文物.org\">古墓文物</a>\n</p></dd></dl></section><h1>游山玩水-&gt;浙江 </h1><section><p></p></section><h2><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vb1-lHR7kRM\">Chinese Boutique B&amp;B 中國最美民宿: Life Outside of the House - YouTube</a></h2><section><ul><li><p><span class=\"timestamp-wrapper\"><span class=\"timestamp\">[2020-11-30 Mon 17:08]</span></span> &lt;- <a href=\"id:40f4c77b-6871-483f-a378-a100449776af\">莫干山镇</a>\n</p></li></ul><div class=\"videoWrapper mb-4\">\n  <iframe\n    src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vb1-lHR7kRM\"\n    width=\"653\"\n    height=\"367\"\n    frameborder=\"0\"\n    allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\"\n    allowfullscreen>\n  </iframe>\n</div>\n</section><h2><a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%25E5%259C%2586%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%259B%25AD/17330161?fromtitle=%25E5%259C%2586%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%259B%25AD&amp;fromid=17247684\">圆明新园（浙江横店圆明新园）<sub>百度百科</sub></a></h2><section><ul><li><p><span class=\"timestamp-wrapper\"><span class=\"timestamp\">[2020-11-30 Mon 17:01]</span></span> &lt;- <a href=\"id:f851dc8f-e8be-4be9-9619-bced66bba2c1\">横店镇</a>\n</p></li></ul></section><h2>丽水站</h2><section><p>丽水站位于中国浙江省丽水市莲都区水东区块，建于 1997 年，是新金温铁路、金温货线上的中间站和二等客、货运站，距离金华站 126 公里，离温州站 136 公里。车站代码 98040。全站客货运开办 24 小时昼夜服务，日均客流大致在 8, 000 左右。\n</p></section><h1>游山玩水-&gt;云南</h1><section><ul><li><p><span class=\"timestamp-wrapper\"><span class=\"timestamp\">[2020-11-30 Mon 17:02]</span></span> &lt;- <a href=\"id:1ecc35c9-e3cf-49f8-8c1a-4975bd1632bb\">云南</a>\n</p></li></ul></section><h2><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CIZZiV7knVM\">民宿｜200 戶人的島上，這家小民宿卻來了 8000 多人 - YouTube</a> 民宿:</h2><section><ul><li><p><span class=\"timestamp-wrapper\"><span class=\"timestamp\">[2020-11-30 Mon 22:24]</span></span> -&gt; <a href=\"id:2fa03fb1-e5de-4068-8719-9fa46bb84ad1\">洱海</a>\n</p></li></ul><div class=\"videoWrapper mb-4\">\n  <iframe\n    src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/CIZZiV7knVM\"\n    width=\"653\"\n    height=\"367\"\n    frameborder=\"0\"\n    allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\"\n    allowfullscreen>\n  </iframe>\n</div>\n</section><h2>摩梭人 </h2><section><ul><li><p><span class=\"timestamp-wrapper\"><span class=\"timestamp\">[2020-11-30 Mon 15:48]</span></span> &lt;- <a href=\"id:b2544e13-2358-4a61-a0f1-27e3afd9271d\">泸沽湖</a>\n</p></li></ul><p>摩梭人主要居住于中国四川省凉山彝族自治州盐源县和木里县与云南省丽江市宁蒗彝族自治县之间的泸沽湖畔，自称“纳”、“纳日”、“纳恒”等。云南摩梭人被划为纳西族，四川摩梭人被劃为蒙古族。截至 2007 年，摩梭人共有 4 万左右人口。\n</p></section><h2><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l-E95bDiGHg\">中国独树一帜的秘境酒店！ - YouTube</a> </h2><section><ul><li><p><span class=\"timestamp-wrapper\"><span class=\"timestamp\">[2020-11-30 Mon 22:16]</span></span> -&gt; <a href=\"id:aa63df48-04d9-4525-8aed-6ee11a89a983\">香格里拉市</a>\n</p></li></ul><div class=\"videoWrapper mb-4\">\n  <iframe\n    src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/l-E95bDiGHg\"\n    width=\"653\"\n    height=\"367\"\n    frameborder=\"0\"\n    allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\"\n    allowfullscreen>\n  </iframe>\n</div>\n</section><h1>游山玩水-&gt;山西</h1><section><ul><li><p><span class=\"timestamp-wrapper\"><span class=\"timestamp\">[2020-11-30 Mon 15:35]</span></span> &lt;- <a href=\"id:f658b210-e699-43d2-acd1-e246056842d7\">山西</a>\n</p></li></ul></section><h2><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PiIWla8mXuU\">“中國第一國寶，藏在山西深山 - YouTube”🔊</a></h2><section><ul><li><p><span class=\"timestamp-wrapper\"><span class=\"timestamp\">[2020-11-30 Mon 22:18]</span></span> -&gt; <a href=\"id:d72fd310-ede1-49b9-942e-42a9010394ea\">佛光寺 (五台)</a>\n</p></li></ul><div class=\"videoWrapper mb-4\">\n  <iframe\n    src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/PiIWla8mXuU\"\n    width=\"653\"\n    height=\"367\"